sec.title: Ethics approval and consent to participate
sec.p: Not applicable. German public health institute (RKI) is authorized to receive blood residuals from diagnostics for surveillance purposes (Infection Protection Act IfSG §13). All samples analysed were anonymised.

sec.title: Competing interests
sec.p: The authors declare that they have no competing interests. The funders had no role in the design of the study; in the collection, analyses, or interpretation of data; in the writing of the manuscript, and in the decision to publish the results.
